# A [[mixture]] of two things, generally in about [[equal]] [[proportion]]s.
## {{label|en|US}} A mixture of [[cream]] and [[milk]] often used in [[coffee]], defined by the US Food and Drug Administration to contain between 10.5% and 18% milk fat.
## A mixture of two [[alcoholic]] [[beverage]]s, most frequently those [[brew#Verb|brewed]] from [[malt]], such as [[porter]] and [[ale]] or [[mild]] and [[bitter]] [[beer]]s, in about equal parts; also used for equal parts of an alcoholic beverage and [[water]].
## A person of [[mixed-race]] or with [[dual]] [[nationality]].
## {{label|en|British}} A combination of both [[rice]] and [[chip]]s as an accompaniment to a [[curry]], as opposed to one or the other.
## {{label|en|UK}} A combination of [[beer]] and [[ale]] (or similar alcoholic drinks) in equal quantities.
## Both [[oral sex]] and [[vaginal sex]] performed in sequence by a [[prostitute]]
## {{label|en|US}} A mixture of half [[lemonade]] and half [[iced tea]].

